    <h2>Help & Support</h2>
    <div class="help-section">
        <h3>Welcome to Pahanaedu Bookshop Management System!</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Login:</strong> Enter your username and password to access the system.</li>
            <li><strong>Main Menu:</strong> Choose from cards to Add/Manage Customers, Add/View Items, Start Orders, View Order History, or see Help.</li>
            <li><strong>Manage Customers:</strong> Add new customers, search, edit, and delete existing ones.</li>
            <li><strong>Add Items:</strong> Add new bookshop items, update or remove them, and search by item name.</li>
            <li><strong>Start Order:</strong> Search items, add them to cart with a specific quantity (not exceeding available stock), and proceed to checkout.</li>
            <li><strong>Cart & Checkout:</strong> Change quantities, remove items, enter customer phone, auto-fill or register new customers, and complete order.</li>
            <li><strong>Order History:</strong> Search and filter past orders by customer or date, and delete old orders if needed.</li>
        </ul>
